 28/9/18 Doingt ? Le Mesnil A dull showeri unpleas and cold day . Got the QM and the Sergeant Cook up and vent my spleen on them for not have tea readi for the troop last night . Rain fell near all the morn and made the chalki ground unpleas slipperi . The men all in littl trench shelter cover bivouac in the trench . Behind us we have Peronn on the left is the famous Mont St Quentin show veri visibl evid of the batter it got that memor afternoon when our lad went into it . Doingt surround by hospit and camp is just ahead of us . Roll bare down all round give great field of fire for Lewi gun or German machin gun . The Gener came round and told me that we shift on
